				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-tag-links">Tagged</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/big-brother" rel="tag">Big Brother</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/breasts" rel="tag">breasts</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/civil-liberties-2" rel="tag">civil liberties</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/edward-snowden" rel="tag">Edward Snowden</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/gchq" rel="tag">GCHQ</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/leap" rel="tag">LEAP</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/nsa" rel="tag">NSA</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/police-2" rel="tag">police</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/privacy" rel="tag">privacy</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/rights" rel="tag">rights</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/surveillance-2" rel="tag">surveillance</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/un" rel="tag">UN</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/whistleblowers-2" rel="tag">whistleblowers</a>			</span>
						
