				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-tag-links">Tagged</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/accountability-2" rel="tag">accountability</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/democracy-2" rel="tag">democracy</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/drugs" rel="tag">drugs</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/iceland" rel="tag">Iceland</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/internet-freedoms" rel="tag">internet freedoms</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/leap" rel="tag">LEAP</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/prohibition" rel="tag">prohibition</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/war-on-drugs" rel="tag">war on drugs</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/war-on-terror" rel="tag">war on terror</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/war-on-terrorism" rel="tag">war on terrorism</a>			</span>
						
