												<span class="cat-links">
				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-cat-links">Posted in</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/afghanistan" title="View all posts in Afghanistan" rel="category tag">Afghanistan</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/drugs-2" title="View all posts in Drugs" rel="category tag">Drugs</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/economics" title="View all posts in Economics" rel="category tag">Economics</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/law" title="View all posts in Law" rel="category tag">Law</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/leap" title="View all posts in LEAP" rel="category tag">LEAP</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/police" title="View all posts in Police" rel="category tag">Police</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/politics" title="View all posts in Politics" rel="category tag">Politics</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/prohibition-2" title="View all posts in Prohibition" rel="category tag">Prohibition</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/talks-2" title="View all posts in Talks" rel="category tag">Talks</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/terrorism" title="View all posts in Terrorism" rel="category tag">Terrorism</a>			</span>
